@apiUrl =  https://fw-teaching.fi/demo/wdbocms/api/v1/products/

### get all products
GET {{apiUrl}}


### get one product by id 


GET {{apiUrl}}1001

### create a new product

POST {{apiUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jeans",
    "price": 100
}

### update a single field in product

PATCH {{apiUrl}}1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 120
}

### change all data in product

PUT {{apiUrl}}1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Shirt",
    "price": 130
}

### delete a product

DELETE {{apiUrl}}1003





